Tu objetivo es Sha Xiaofei.

00:16:56.560 --> 00:16:59.200
Deja a Duan Qing y al capitán Xia
vaya a Jiang Jiuping.

00:16:59.480 --> 00:16:59.960
Sí.

00:17:00.360 --> 00:17:01.888
Adelante. Pronto.

00:17:08.000 --> 00:17:09.640
¿Qué hizo mi padre?

00:17:10.880 --> 00:17:11.680
Jiang.

00:17:12.440 --> 00:17:13.880
Dile.

00:17:17.960 --> 00:17:18.640
Nana.

00:17:20.680 --> 00:17:23.800
Tu padre no es el hombre que crees que es.

00:17:24.560 --> 00:17:25.720
Tu padre

00:17:25.720 --> 00:17:27.880
